column2: SELECT s.mjd, s.plate, s.fiberID, s.z as z FROM WISE_xmatch AS x JOIN WISE_allsky AS w ON x.wise_cntr = w.cntr JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS p ON x.sdss_objid = p.objid JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON s.specobjid = p.specobjid WHERE (s.class = # or s.class = #) AND p.nChild = # AND p.dered_g > # AND p.dered_z > # AND p.dered_r > # AND s.z < # AND s.snmedian_g > # AND s.snmedian_r > # ORDER BY s.z DESC
